    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in poor condition \u2014 buyers should be fully aware of what they're getting before making a purchase. The exterior shows significant wear including multiple scratches, dents, and paint fading throughout. The interior has considerable damage including torn upholstery, worn surfaces, and non-functional components. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require serious attention and repair investment \u2014 it is not currently in reliable driving condition. This listing is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a major restoration project, a parts vehicle, or someone with mechanical expertise looking for a fixer-upper. No attempt has been made to conceal or minimize the car's condition \u2014 what you see is what you get, and a thorough pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged.",
